00:03:46.010 --> 00:03:49.070 position:56%
and What are The Blind Men Dreaming?

00:03:49.070 --> 00:03:54.540
And to think about the title of
the book and also asking Noemi,

00:03:54.540 --> 00:04:00.250
what way are you dreaming or made
