relationship with the dreams

00:08:40.790 --> 00:08:45.200
and the unconscious or some
experience that we have in life

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:48.690
that brings through, that's
kind of transformed, you know,

00:08:48.690 --> 00:08:52.380
our conscious to dreams
good or bad experiences.

00:08:52.380 --> 00:08:56.160
And also, the place of
literature as a place, you know,

00:08:56.160 --> 00:08:59.320
