00:11:42.730 --> 00:11:48.560
You cannot make her
remember something casual.

00:11:49.580 --> 00:11:52.410
It's all that's written
in the diary.

00:11:52.410 --> 00:11:59.630 position:56%
So I think it was a way for her to
deposit her memories somewhere else.

00:11:59.630 --> 00:12:02.550
That's how I interpret it.

00:12:02.550 --> 00:12:06.580
But for me, I think
I became a writer,

00:12:06.580 --> 00:12:11.220
