00:12:11.220 --> 00:12:15.050
I knew I wanted to become a writer.

00:12:15.050 --> 00:12:16.750
That was the dream of my life.

00:12:16.750 --> 00:12:19.130
Talking about dreams, right?

00:12:19.130 --> 00:12:21.280
That was a dream of my life.

00:12:21.280 --> 00:12:23.280
I invented books.

00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:27.620
I read from books without
knowing how to read.

00:12:27.620 --> 00:12:30.110
I opened books, and I
