00:13:55.620 --> 00:14:01.190
I think now I can start
writing about other things.

00:14:01.190 --> 00:14:04.220
And it was very therapeutic
to me, too.

00:14:04.220 --> 00:14:06.240
&gt;&gt; Vivaldo dos Santos: And how
