00:15:03.110 --> 00:15:04.410
&gt;&gt; Noemi Jaffe: Third person.

00:15:04.410 --> 00:15:05.710
&gt;&gt; Vivaldo dos Santos:
Like the daughter.

00:15:05.710 --> 00:15:09.160
Could you tell a little
bit about that, please?

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:12.460
&gt;&gt; Noemi Jaffe: That was a very
