00:15:12.460 --> 00:15:17.530
because when I started writing my
part of the book, I was writing it

00:15:17.530 --> 00:15:22.010
in the first person, because it's
about the story of my mother,

00:15:22.010 --> 00:15:27.220
about my life, my sisters'
lives, my opinions.

00:15:27.220 --> 00:15:30.540
But I wasn't feeling
comfortable with it,

00:15:30.540 --> 00:15:33.930
