to be so truthful.

00:15:53.830 --> 00:16:00.350
I wanted to be able to fictionalize
little, and then I tried.

00:16:00.350 --> 00:16:03.060
I made an experiment to
write it in third person,

00:16:03.060 --> 00:16:08.400
and as soon as I began,
I felt so much more free.

00:16:08.400 --> 00:16:13.700
When I started writing in the
third person, I could invent more.

00:16:13.700 --> 00:16:19.020
I could acquire a little
more distance towards myself.

00:16:19.020 --> 00:16:23.550
I felt I wasn't in the
