mother is also a desire

00:54:02.990 --> 00:54:07.670
to eradicate her suffering from
our memories so that she, herself,

00:54:07.670 --> 00:54:14.510
can be freed of it, so that
she can live without the stone.

00:54:14.510 --> 00:54:20.040
